logic.roles.taskroles

Class Worker

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.roles.Role
      • logic.roles.taskroles.Worker
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Supervisor

    public class Worker
extends Role
    Base role for completing jobs. Can only belong to one task at any given time and has many jobs to mark as done.
